Usage: add_sai_boundary_flops [-help] [-clock <string>] [-delete_flops]
                              -hinsts <string> -ports <string> [-ref_flop <string> [-clock_input_pin <string>] [-data_input_pin <string>] [-data_output_pin <string>]]

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
-clock <string>               # Specifies module's clock port name
                              # (string, optional)
-clock_input_pin <string>     # Specify cell CLK port name (string, optional)
-data_input_pin <string>      # Specify cell D port name (string, optional)
-data_output_pin <string>     # Specify cell Q port name (string, optional)
-delete_flops                 # remove all flops which are added
                              # (bool, optional)
-hinsts <string>              # Specifies the module name (string, required)
-ports <string>               # Specifies module pin name (string, required)
-ref_flop <string>            # Specify the flop cell name to be inserted along
                              # the boundary (string, optional)